<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<style>
* {
box-sizing: border-box;
}




body {
font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}




/* Style the header */
header {
background-color: blue;
padding: 30px;
text-align: center;
font-size: 35px;
color: white;
}




/* Create two columns/boxes that floats next to each other */
nav {
float: left;
width: 30%;
height: 400px; /* only for demonstration, should be removed */
background: rgb(12, 12, 12);
padding: 20px;
}




/* Style the list inside the menu */
nav ul {
list-style-type: none;
padding: 0;
}




article {
float: left;
padding: 20px;
width: 70%;
background-color: lightblue;
height: 400px; /* only for demonstration, should be removed */
}




/* Clear floats after the columns */
section::after {
content: "";
display: table;
clear: both;
}




/* Style the footer */
footer {
background-color: blue;
padding: 10px;
text-align: center;
color: white;
}




/* Responsive layout - makes the two columns/boxes stack on top of each other instead of next to each other, on small screens */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
nav, article {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}
}
</style>




</head>
<body>








<header>
<h4>All About Vincent James Hidden Genius Student</h4>
</header>




<section>
<nav>
  <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTVEbrH6KAKBwWh2HxGCFxmjR1KBpE9vEurKoedbyWjyQ&s=10"
 alt="Mountain" width="175" height="150">
  <ul>
      <img src="https://www.straightofficial.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/NBA2-1.jpg" width="175" height="150">
  <ul>




</nav>
 <article>
  <h1>My name is Vincent. I am an active and motivated person who enjoys sports, fishing, and fitness. I play basketball for UYK&Q (Urban Youth Kings & Queens), and I also play at the YMCA. In my free time, I enjoy fishing at ponds and lakes because it helps me relax and enjoy nature. When I'm not using my phone, I like to stay productive by doing push-ups and other exercises at home. I enjoy challenging myself, staying active, and working hard to improve every day.</h1>




</article>
</section>




<footer>
<p> My Look Alikes: Big Sean & NBA Youngboy</p>
</footer>


</body>
</html>


